## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources accessed. Some sources may not have been updated recently, which could affect the relevance of the information. Additionally, the focus was primarily on English-language sources, which may exclude valuable insights from non-English publications. Further research could expand on these findings by incorporating a broader range of international perspectives and more recent studies.

